`\r\n\r\nWhich is different from what ReactJS's semantic [1]\r\n\r\n> Render a React element into the DOM in the supplied container and return a reference to the component (or returns null for stateless components).\r\n\r\nThe current approach by returning a `Native` is just a workaround, so we will fix this by returning:\r\n\r\n* the actual ruby instance if your are render a custom component\r\n* the actual DOM node if you are render a dom component\r\n\r\n[1] https://facebook.github.io/react/docs/react-dom.html#render","score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ruby-hyperloop/hyper-react/issues/186","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ruby-hyperloop/hyper-react","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ruby-hyperloop/hyper-react/issues/186/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ruby-hyperloop/hyper-react/issues/186/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ruby-hyperloop/hyper-react/issues/186/events","html_url":"https://github.com/ruby-hyperloop/hyper-react/issues/186","id":190565133,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWUxOTA1NjUxMzM=","number":186,"title":"Extract render_to_static_markup & render_to_string to React::Server module","user":{"login":"zetachang","id":839973,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjgzOTk3Mw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/839973?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/zetachang","html_url":"https://github.com/zetachang","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zetachang/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zetachang/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zetachang/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zetachang/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zetachang/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zetachang/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zetachang/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/zetachang/events{/privacy}",